README
2019 March 28, Aaron Tran

Quick guide to provenance of different files.  Often, people modify FLASH
source code to get the job done.  My goal is to take those pieces out and place
in Simulation problem, to better elucidate code dependencies and structure, and
to ward off possible conflicts / unexpected source code overrides (e.g.,
conflicts between two units' different prescriptions of zoom-in refinement).

~------------------------------------------------------------------------------

